{"pageProps":{"note":{"id":"6e2ho1hbe3wrt78uo63bkix","title":"Docker","desc":"","updated":1699585576527,"created":1699585243723,"custom":{},"fname":"programing.docker","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":".","selfContained":true,"name":"docs"},"contentHash":"f0093aff9ad2d6a151f3a2889bf75292","links":[],"anchors":{"lightweight-containerization":{"type":"header","text":"Lightweight containerization","value":"lightweight-containerization","line":10,"column":0,"depth":2},"application-packaging":{"type":"header","text":"Application packaging","value":"application-packaging","line":18,"column":0,"depth":2},"kubernetes-k8s":{"type":"header","text":"Kubernetes (K8s)","value":"kubernetes-k8s","line":24,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":[],"parent":"4qi2z0z9fquupbd651xausx","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"docker\">Docker<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#docker\"></a></h1>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://blog.bytebytego.com/p/a-crash-course-in-docker\">https://blog.bytebytego.com/p/a-crash-course-in-docker</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"lightweight-containerization\">Lightweight containerization<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#lightweight-containerization\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>The Docker engine does not virtualize OS resources\n<ul>\n<li>container achieve isolation through <strong>Linux namespaces &#x26; control groups</strong></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Namespaces: separation for processes, networking, mounts,...</li>\n<li>cgroups (control groups): limit &#x26; meter usages of resources</li>\n<li>=> Sharing the OS kernel, not the host physical resources</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"application-packaging\">Application packaging<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#application-packaging\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Docker is solving \n<ul>\n<li>Bundling the app, configs, dependencies &#x26; OS -> single image</li>\n<li>Remain the environments (dev, runtime)</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"kubernetes-k8s\">Kubernetes (K8s)<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#kubernetes-k8s\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Cluster management taking advantages of the Docker engine</li>\n</ul>","noteIndex":{"id":"xfkxbponh0sohobo6pual15","title":"Root","desc":"","updated":1668137379975,"created":1663481872547,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"root","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":".","selfContained":true,"name":"docs"},"contentHash":"cb44915142ec96bef8f764f3dc90389e","links":[],"anchors":{"welcome-to-my-page":{"type":"header","text":"Welcome to my page","value":"welcome-to-my-page","line":7,"column":0,"depth":1},"contacts":{"type":"header","text":"Contacts","value":"contacts","line":12,"column":0,"depth":2},"dendron":{"type":"header","text":"Dendron","value":"dendron","line":18,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":["u5a2e2vvfn3x7k0shuvmb1b","qw8y69zxn8wr7tzz4gtcrrv","q7qw45jglqwmynary64q67c","6wjqcjgkrpeqtmzb1o8o1q8","3ervbn5we7t8v2l2vwtx847","4qi2z0z9fquupbd651xausx","sencgim78q74o1zuyvy1vz7","ue4oml1si982t3mmbthyxi9","zrogwjgtze8ne5joqpz8ty9","oesia0lbzh03fsoy124ck0k","el3p9zjue6h3b6zsl9oejkt","t5grkmcwvu4nl43igsj4gxz"],"parent":null,"data":{},"body":"# Welcome to my page\n\n- This is a place where I write my knowledge in both Vietnamese and English.\n- Please feel free to correct me if there is anything not right.\n\n## Contacts\n\n- [Github](https://github.com/thanhpp)\n- [Discord](https://discord.gg/ugNRjFNqjp)\n- [LinkedIn](https://www.linkedin.com/in/thanhpp/)\n\n## Dendron\n\n- [Home Page](https://wiki.dendron.so/)"},"collectionChildren":null,"customHeadContent":null,"config":{"version":5,"dev":{"enablePreviewV2":true,"enableSelfContainedVaults":true},"commands":{"lookup":{"note":{"selectionMode":"extract","confirmVaultOnCreate":true,"vaultSelectionModeOnCreate":"alwaysPrompt","leaveTrace":false,"bubbleUpCreateNew":true,"fuzzThreshold":0.2}},"randomNote":{},"insertNoteLink":{"aliasMode":"none","enableMultiSelect":false},"insertNoteIndex"